            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Combine the <strong>coconut yoghurt</strong>,<strong> chopped ginger</strong>, <strong>ground turmeric</strong> and <strong>curry powder</strong> in a large bowl</p>\n<p>Add a generous drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil</strong> and a pinch of<strong> salt</strong> – this is your <strong>tandoori marinade</strong></p>\n<p>Using clean hands, add the <strong>cauliflower wedges</strong> to the <strong>tandoori marinade</strong> and give it a good mix up until fully covered in marinade</p>",
